     "_comment_": "macOS EXAMPLE -- not loaded by Claude Code (filename is not .mcp.json). Copy to .mcp.json (after backing up the Windows version) to run on macOS. Only difference vs the Windows .mcp.json: command uses .venv/bin/python instead of .venv/Scripts/python.exe.",

